originalText.text: Aleta is so special and amazing!!! I've spoken to other healers in the past, but nobody compares to Aleta!! She is a warm, compassionate and gifted spiritual healer who always makes time for you and actually produces results! She listens very closely so that she can fully understand your mind and body and then teaches you the skills you need to manifest your life's intentions! She can literally help you shift your mindset to enable you to make your dreams come true! Highly recommend Aleta! Her positive thinking and strong, manifesting energy will change your life forever!!

originalText.text: Aleta is a one of a kind psycho-spiritual healer and life coach. She exudes love in everything she says and does. She truly cares! She is the “real deal”! If you are interested in living a more fulfilled and joyful life, I highly recommend you go see her. She uses her own unique blend of powerful “energy tools” to help you release any underlying emotions, beliefs and thought patterns that are keeping you stuck while helping you shift to become your most authentic self. Her work has been highly effective and transformational for me personally in terms of regaining my health and starting an entire new business! Not only has Aleta become my trusted advisor but also she has become a dear friend.

originalText.text: Aleta is an angel from heaven sent with gifts and healing abilities only experiencing firsthand one can believe. Her soothing aura and compassionate nature only further enhances your experience with each and every session. Her abilities help you to navigate through any rough patch, help heal any past trauma affecting your present, and most importantly her channels help you present day truly create the life you’ve always imagined and dreamed about. I would highly recommend her to any and everyone because just being in presence is truly a healing gift in itself. Thank you Aleta!

originalText.text: I was born a skeptic on all fronts-  but after my first session,  I genuinely believe that Aleta has a truly special gift. I left the session feeling so much lighter, both mentally and physically. I went into the session to address a specific issue, and she was able to find the source of my stress- which until then, I hadn't been able to pinpoint- and help me release it. Her psychic and empathic energies are undeniable. I feel lucky to have found her!

originalText.text: I started working with Aleta  St. James to help me shift into a new life pattern after going through a divorce and a being laid off from my job. In less than a year I have created my own business and started working with students and clients. I've also found a new friendship that is true to my nature. The inner work that Aleta unleashes through multiple ways (sound, light, energy, earth crystals) which have made a difference in how I view the things I want to allow in my life.
